dct_description_sm: de novo accuratè in lucem editae: per Nicolaum I. Piscatorem.
Bar scale on map given in "Milliaria Germanica"; bar scale on inset map given in "Milliaria communia Germanica".
North oriented toward right of sheet.
Decorative cartouches, coat of arms, figure holding bar scale.
Inset map: Vt. Iuliacensium atque Cliviensium Regiones...
